== Description ==

The '''BIM Unclone''' tool converts a [[BIM_Clone|clone]] object into an independent copy of the original objects. The resulting object is no longer linked to the original. Changes to the original will not affect the uncloned copy, and vice versa.

== Usage ==

# Select a single clone object in the [[3D_View|3D View]] or the [[Tree_View|Tree View]].
# Select the {{MenuCommand|Utils → [[Image:BIM_Unclone.svg|16px]] Unclone}} option from the menu.
# The clone is replaced with an independent copy of its original object.

== Notes ==

* Uncloned objects may still share their {{PropertyData|Base}} property with the original object, making them not fully independent.


